Name: Spencer and a Show
Title: Kalbi Beef Ribs; Shishito Peppers; Candied Nuts; Crab Cakes With Curry Herb Dip
Desc: Recipes for kalbi beef ribs, shishito peppers, candied nuts and crab cakes with a curry herb dip.
LongDescription: Chef Spencer Watts shares his recipe for sweet and sticky kalbi style beef ribs, whips up blistered shishito peppers with a homemade aioli, sweet and crunchy candied nuts with just a hint of spice and crabs cakes with an aromatic curry herb dip.
